        Matt. 14:19.</char>
    </note>
    <note caller="[i]" style="f">
      <char style="fk">[i]</char>
      <char style="ft"><char style="it">designed teachers</char>…Lit: <char style="it">Scribes</char></char>
    </note>
    <note caller="[j]" style="f">
      <char style="fk">[j]</char>
      <char style="ft"><char style="it">live it up</char>…Lit: <char style="it">eat and drink. </char>An idiom.</char>
