    <note caller="[k]" style="f">
      <char style="fk">[k]</char>
      <char style="ft"><char style="it">and you shall have eternal life</char>…Lit: <char style="it">and you shall live</char>.
        Based on the context, the latter phrase is understood to mean the former.</char>
