    <note caller="[v]" style="f">
      <char style="fk">[v]</char>
      <char style="ft"><char style="it">you know how to discern the patterns of land and sky</char>…Lit: <char style="it">you
        know to discern the face </char>[<char style="it">countenance</char>]<char style="it"> of the land and
        of the sky</char>. Jesus speaks as though the land and sky are living beings which decide by themselves
