    <note caller="[A]" style="f">
      <char style="fk">[A]</char>
      <char style="ft"><char style="it">bright, colorful, beautiful clothing</char>…In ancient times, kings, noblemen, and the
        rich were distinguished from the peasants by wearing this sort of clothing; hence Herod’s mocking of
        Jesus’s kingship.</char>
    </note>
    <note caller="[B]" style="f">
      <char style="fk">[B]</char>
